quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  76,26,"Innu Mbo e juulɗeele ɗiɗe jemma: Futura e geeƴe, hinkaƴina caggal majje."
  76,27,"Ɓe sirkuɓe na yiɗi nguurndam aduna hoɓe ndeerɗi e majjam, hoɓe ngacca caggal mum e ñande darnga, oon ko nisɗo, sabu ko woni ko e hembo e caɗeele."
  76,28,"Ko Minen tagi on Min cemmbiniri tagu mon semmbinde jokkorɗe mon e tere mon, si Min faalaama halkude on Min ngosto toon yeru mon, Min kalka on Min ngosto mon."
  76,29,"Nde simoore konde waajo e siftanirde, kala faalaaɗo nanngude laawol yottaade e weluya Alla nannga ngol."
  76,30,"On faaletaake nanngude laawol peewal si wonah Alla faalanee on ɗuum, fof ko e Alla ruttato, Alla na anndi ko moƴƴanta jiyaaɓe Makko, e ko moƴƴaani e mum en, ko O ñeeña e tagu Makko e hoddira e sariya Makko."
  76,31,"Hombo naatna mbo O wela e jiyaaɓe Makko e yurmeende Makko, O hawrinaɓe e iimaan e golle moƴƴe, O heblani tooñruɓe ɓe pittaali mum en keefeeru e goopi lepte muusɗe ka laakara, ko ɗuum woni lepte yiite."
  77,1,"Alla woondirii keneeli dewandirɗi hono siiru puccu."
  77,2,"O woondiri keneeli bippooji bippugol."
  77,3,"O woondiri keneeli carooji toɓo cargol."
  77,4,"O wooniri malayke en tellinooji ko seernata hakkunde goongo e meere."
  77,5,"O woondiri malayka en tellinooji wahyu."
  77,6,"Hoɗi tellina wahyu okkoowo ngantu ummaade ka Alla faade e aade en e jeertinde ɓe lepte Alla."
  77,7,"Ko podante ɗon ko e ummital e haasbeede e njoɓdi ko ko arata sikke alah heen."
  77,8,"Si annoore koode e ndaaygu mum momtaama."
  77,9,"Si kammu on fettii sabi tellaade Malayka en e mammba."
  77,10,"Si pelle ɗuggitaama e nokku mum en ɗe kelta haa ngonti sollaaru."
  77,11,"Saanga nde Nelaaɓe ndennina e waktu dottaaɗo."
  77,12,"ñalawma mawɗo dirtinaama ngam seedaade e leƴƴi mum en."
  77,13,"E ñalngu ceerndugol hakkunde jiyaaɓe, feeña hakkunde mbo goonga e mbo meere, e malaaɗo e kiitaaɗo."
  77,14,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaaɗo-ko woni ñalngu ceerndugol."
  77,15,"Halkaare e lepte e perte e oon ñalawma woodanii fennuɓe ko nelaaɓe ngaddi ummaade ka Alla."
  77,16,"Mbela Min kalkaana leƴƴi gadinooɗi nde njedduno penni Nulaaɓe mum en?."
  77,17,"Refti Min bndewna heen cakkatiiɓe ɓe, Min kalkaɓe no Min kalkiri mon nih."
  77,18,"Ko hono no Min kalkiri ɗiin leƴƴi, Min kalkirta fennuɓe ko Nelaaɗo addi ko."
  77,19,"Halkaare e lepte woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe njbdi mum en ñande ñalngu njoɓdi."